Suluku kɛna wonu ŋgʊ kɩkpakʊ ɛyaa nɛ kutuluu tadɩyɛ wondu yɔ. Kɩɩɖɔŋ haba yɔɔ ɛzɩ lɔɔɖa yɔ, ɛlɛ kpasɩ yɔɔ kiduu sɩɖɩsɩɖɩ. Suluku wɛna pilima sakɩyɛ nɛ a-taa kɛ paɖʊʊ tadɩyɛ wondu ndɩ ndɩ. Pilima ana a-ɛsɩnda lɛ, mɔɔʊ nakʊyʊ wɛɛ nɛ ŋgʊ hɔŋna-wɛ. Ɖooo pɩnaɣ 1804 kɛ kacalaɣ suluku kpayaɣ ɖa ɖɔm kɛ Kewiyaɣ kɩkpɛndaɣ ɛjaɖɛ taa ɖenɖe payaɣ se Galɩ yɔ. Pɩɩkɛna suluku kpayaɣ ŋga kalakaɣ tʊmɩyɛ nɛ miŋ feveku yɔ. Weyi payaɣ se Richard  Trevithick yɔ eelubina-kʊ Merthyr Tydfil tɛtʊ taa. Paapɩzɩʊ pasaa suluku kpayaɣ kɛ paale yem. Pɩpɔzʊ se pɩkɛna kpayɩsɩ yɔɔ. Mbʊ yebina n,e payaɣ-kʊ se suluku kpayaɣ. 
Sulukiŋ wɛna huwa naatozo pɩlɩɩna ɩ-tʊma labʊ taa. Nɩɩyɛ ɖɔŋna sɩŋgʊ sɩŋgʊ. Lɛɛŋ ñasɩŋgʊ nɩmayasa sɔsɔna taa nɛ lɛɛŋ lɛ, ɩɩtɩɩsɩŋgʊ ɖoli yee pɩtɛkɛ ɖenɖe ɩwokɩ yɔ kɔƴɔ.
